Enumeration RuntimeType

An enum to indicate current runtime type, both web page (running in a browser) and wechat mini game (https://developers.weixin.qq.com/minigame/dev/guide/) are supported, toutiao mini game (https://developer.toutiao.com/) will be supported soon.
